<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.8.6">
<l>viṭaṅkalan tamarnta varavaṇait tuyiṉṟu viḷaṅkaṉik kiḷaṅkaṉṟu viciṟi</l>
<l>kuṭaṅkalan tāṭik kuravaimuṉ kōtta kūttavem maṭikaḷtam kōyil</l>
<l>taṭaṅkaṭal mukantu vicumpiṭaip piḷiṟat taṭavaraik kaḷiṟeṉṟu muṉintu</l>
<l>maṭaṅkalniṉ ṟatirum māliruñ cōlai vaṇaṅkutum vāmaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Come, simple heart; we will worship in Māliruñcōlai where,</l>
<l rend="indent">when the heavenly realm rumbles, having taken up water</l>
<l rend="indent">from the vast sea,</l>
<l>Lions roar, standing [their ground], raging, imagining</l>
<l rend="indent">huge, mountain elephants,</l>
<l>The temple of our dancer god who once locked [hands] in the kuravai</l>
<l rend="indent">having danced, spinning pots,</l>
<l>And having hurled a young calf for woodapples,</l>
<l rend="indent">and slept on a reclining snake bed, swirling the waters.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
